    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the lower panels. Mechanically, the engine requires major repairs to be roadworthy, and the interior has sustained heavy wear with tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is priced to reflect its current state and will need to be towed.",
